Sukriti Gumber Feb . 21 . 2017 Shruti Haasan with Michael Corsale 
Shruti Haasan was spotted last evening at the Mumbai airport along with her rumoured boyfriend, Michael Corsale . Although Shruti denied dating this hottie in the recent past, reports suggest that the duo was in Rishikesh for a romantic getaway. Meanwhile, we think Shruti and Michael make a stunning couple.
